<p>Not every business needs the same stack. The right tool combination depends on your size, your budget, and where your customers are in their decision-making journey when they find you.</p>
<h3>Solo operator or single-location business</h3>
<p><strong>Budget ceiling:</strong> $150-200/month</p>
<p><strong>Priority order:</strong>
1. Google Business Profile (free — optimize this first)
